parameters: \n< Erika >How about that! Did you see it!!!

\n< Erika >How about it! What do you think of the taste of my
right arm, Mr. Minotaur!
\n< Serena >Erika... I apologize, I made a mistake.
\n< Serena >For my sake, my right arm...

\n< Serena >...Are you still alive, Mr. Minotaur? Your
vitality is quite astonishing.

\n< Serena >...However, with those wounds, it's unlikely
you'll survive. If you truly wish for a quiet
death, I have no intention of pursuing you...
\n< Serena >...It seems you're not in the mood. Very well.
\n< Serena >My name is Serena Fuoco L'Brillante Della Grazia.

\n< Serena >The last bloodline of the old empire... and my
proud and noble friend, Erika. The sword and
shield of the Erika Lynn route.

\n< Serena >Minotaurus. A soul without a place to belong. An
evil monster.

\n< Serena >The god who rules over this world shall take your
life and bestow upon you a shameful death!
\n< Erika >Guh... S-Serena! Are you okay, Serena!
\n< Erika >Damn it...! The target is Serena...!

\n< Erika >Do you have a preference for blondes? Big sister
was like that too, right...

\n< Erika >Ugh...Shit...Damn it...I just messed up my
insides...

\n< Erika >Haa... Ha... Haha... Hic... Hehehe... Hehehehe...
Hehehehehe...

\n< Erika >Serena behind me. A damn bastard in front of me.
I'm completely beaten up and going crazy all over
the place.
\n< Erika >Isn't it great? I'm getting really excited now.

\n< Erika >Hahaha! Sorryyy! I'm interrupting your meal,
aren't I?!

\n< Erika >But you know... there's a thing called order when
it comes to meals. It's not good manners to
suddenly have the main dish.

\n< Erika >First, it's proper etiquette to start with the
appetizers... I apologize for the appearance, but
this here is my pride and joy...
\n< Erika >I have confidence in the texture, you know!

\n< Erika >What's wrong, what's wrong, you beef bastard! You
said you killed my sister... so I was wondering
what kind of person you are!

\n< Erika >Not at all!... So weak...! Your attacks...! I'll
eat my meal properly.............

\n< Erika >......What the hell is this?!...Hey, what the
fuck?!

\n< Erika >That's right... come at me... don't just stand
there and watch!!

\n< Erika >You... my right arm...!! Youuuuuu! It hurrrrrrts
sooooo much!!
\n< Erika >How dare you!! You fucking ate me!!

\n< Erika >Blood... it's gushing out... Shit... I'm seriously
gonna die...

\n< Erika >Haa... You're eating it so deliciously... It
seriously pisses me off...!

\n< Erika >With this, it's gonna end up being a double
suicide between you and me, dammit!!
\n< Erika >How dare you!! Did you see that!!!

\n< Erika >How about it! How does the taste of my right arm
feel, Mr. Minotaurus!

\n< Erika >Gobo... hehe... Sister's meat... it's definitely
different in taste!!

\n< Erika >I want the trash and scum... to be taken care of
all at once... and feel refreshed... in a good
mood...
\n< Serena >Erika-sama... I apologize, I made a mistake.
\n< Serena >For my sake, my right arm...

\n< Serena >...You're still alive, Mr. Minotaurus. It's quite
an astonishing vitality.

\n< Serena >...However, with those wounds, you won't likely
survive. If you truly wish for a quiet death, I
have no intention of pursuing you...
\n< Serena >...It seems you're not interested. Very well.
\n< Serena >My name is Serena. Fuoco L'Brillante Della Grazia.

\n< Serena >The last bloodline of the old empire... and my
proud and noble friend, Erika. The sword and
shield of the Erika Lynn route.

\n< Serena >Minotaurus. A soul without a place to belong. An
evil monster.

\n< Serena >The god who rules over this world shall take your
life and bestow upon you a shameful death!

\n< Serena >Ugh... My magical power is... I'm sorry, Erika-
sama...
\n< Serena >From here...? In a place like this...?
\n< Serena >......Sound, that is vibration. That is impact.

\n< Serena >I turned your body into an instrument. The melody
of flesh tearing, the rhythm of bones shattering.

\n< Serena >Sound creates sound, and impact generates impact.
There is no longer any way to stop it.
\n< Serena >Be sent to your own body's funeral march and die.

\n< Serena >I may have gone too far... However, now is not the
time to be discouraged.

\n< Serena >Now, let's go back, Erika-sama. It's alright. I
will definitely find a way to handle it.
\n< Serena >I would be troubled if you were to die.
\n< Serena >Because you are my only second friend...
